reviewText: You cant be disappointed with Jeff.  He is always funny, down to earth kind of stuff and always about real life for those of us in the "real world."  Always makes me laugh when he goes on about his family and how things are in the redneck world!  We may not admit it - but we ALL are a redneck in some ways I am sure!
